column16: Ben Francisco singles on a ground ball to left fielder Ryan Roberts.
Carlos Corporan homers (1) on a fly ball to right center field.
Brian Bixler flies out to center fielder Gerardo Parra.
Scott Moore flies out to left fielder Ryan Roberts.
Michael Bourn grounds out to first baseman Paul Goldschmidt.
Tim Hudson out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Gerardo Parra.    Freddie Freeman scores.    Andrelton Simmons to 3rd.
Andrelton Simmons doubles (5) on a soft line drive to right fielder Justin Upton.    Freddie Freeman to 3rd.
Freddie Freeman reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by shortstop Willie Bloomquist.    Dan Uggla scores.
Chipper Jones flies out to left fielder Jason Kubel.    Dan Uggla to 3rd.
Juan Pierre singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Jason Kubel.  Pete Orr out at home on the throw, left fielder Jason Kubel to catcher Miguel Montero.
Pete Orr doubles (2) on a line drive to right fielder Justin Upton.
Freddy Galvis flies out to right fielder Justin Upton.
John Mayberry called out on strikes.
